#h(0em) 8. Ошибки: единый формат {code, message, details}; code — строковый код (BAD_REQUEST, UNAUTHORIZED, FORBIDDEN, NOT_FOUND, CONFLICT, VALIDATION_ERROR, RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED, INTERNAL_ERROR).

